Package: Hurricanes
Type: Package
Title: Hurricanes
Version: 0.0.0.9001
Authors@R: person("Tim", "Trice", email = "tim.trice@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Depends:
  R (>= 3.2.3), 
  magrittr (>= 1.5)
Description: Get archived data of past and current hurricanes for the Atlantic 
  and eastern Pacific oceans.
  This package will also combine HURDAT which was another R library I wrote to 
  get best-track data from the National Hurricane Center.
URL: http://www.timtrice.net
BugReports: https://github.com/timtrice/Hurricanes/issues
